<l>niṉṟa vāytaṅ keṭutal vēṇṭum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The numerals from one to nine when preceding the word <foreign xml:lang="ta">pattu</foreign></l>
<l>' ten ' will have the doubling of the consonant in the middle; the</l>
<l>occuring <foreign xml:lang="ta">āytam</foreign> must disappear.<note
              place="foot">e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">oru+pattu+oṉṟu&gt;oru+paẖtu+oṉṟu&gt;orupattoṉṟu.</foreign></note></l>
